Notes:
OG Filename: That fasho (prod. curesfu;
Alternate Filename: That Fasho [Prod. Curesful]
Dated October 24, 2020 in producer Curesful's files. Previewed by Yeat in a tracklist titled "Tha album" an Instagram post in January 2021 or earlier. Uses a reproduced version of the instrumental of Playboi Carti and RX PESO's unreleased collaboration "Money Over All," originally produced by Pi'erre Bourne. Leaked on February 11, 2022, a week before the release of 2 Alivë.

